Class Position

java.lang.Object
fr.tp.inf112.projects.robotsim.model.Position
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visitable, Serializable
public class Position extends Object implements Visitable, Serializable
Represents a position in a 2D space with x and y coordinates. Provides methods to get and set coordinates, and to enforce limits on the coordinates.
